definition: see 秋高氣爽|秋高气爽[qiu1 gao1 qi4 shuang3]
gas/air/smell/weather/to make angry/to annoy/to get angry/vital energy/qi

sentences.english: Life starts all over again when it gets crisp in the fall.
sentences.chinese: 秋天一到，天高氣爽，生活就又重新開始了。

sentences.english: It is good season too with mild breeze in the day and bright moonlight in the night.
sentences.chinese: 這是一個好季節，天高氣爽，月光明亮。

sentences.english: The spring is warm and moist, while autumn is cool and nice.
sentences.chinese: 春天溫暖溼潤，秋季天高氣爽。
